---
title: Easy Double Chorizo, Potato & Veggie Traybake with Dill-Parsley Mayo & Feta
description: Baking veggies on a tray in the oven, it's a no fuss method to ensure a tonne of flavours all come together. The
chorizo is an addition that we are absolutely sure will knock your socks off!
